<section class="media" id="media">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">In the Media</span>

    <blockquote class="media-item">
      <h2 class="media-headline">
        Profiled by NPR on how federal hiring freezes and policy realignments reshaped
        career plans for the class of 2025.
      </h2>
      <p class="media-cite">
        <span class="media-source">NPR · Education</span> —
